    "Then we selected the top five companies (Amazon, Apple, BYD, GM, Ford) in this ranking together with close price as input to evaluate the model performances in stock forecasting.",
    "Stock Price PredictionThe mean squared error (MSE) is used to evaluate the performance of the models.",
    "MSE is the average squared difference between the observed values and the predicted values.",
    "A smaller MSE indicates better model performance.Table 3 to 10 presents the prediction results in terms of MSE for the eight selected companies.",
    "All values are expressed as percentages."
